	<p>Education, Awareness and Outreach is one of the units that make up the Office of the Vice-President, Equity and Community Inclusion (OVPECI). Led by Crystal Mark, the unit identifies, develops and delivers customized learning solutions to the Ryerson community.&nbsp;</p>
